01:02:35.752 --> 01:02:37.754
Hey, we all make
bad decisions, right?

01:02:37.788 --> 01:02:39.514
Tell me about it.

01:02:41.965 --> 01:02:45.831
Hey, you were so good tonight.
Great. You were great tonight.

01:02:46.970 --> 01:02:48.695
Thank you.

