01:03:28.805 --> 01:03:30.876
This'll make a great picture.

01:03:31.773 --> 01:03:33.154
No.

01:03:33.982 --> 01:03:35.984
No pictures.

01:03:36.019 --> 01:03:38.159
Let's just remember this.

01:03:39.816 --> 01:03:41.852
Can I see you again?

