the house on Sunday.

01:04:47.780 --> 01:04:51.922
And it's my secret place
so we won't get caught.

01:04:51.957 --> 01:04:53.993
We can't get caught.

01:04:54.407 --> 01:04:57.894
So no pictures,
no texts, no calls.

01:04:57.928 --> 01:04:59.930
